                "skills": [
                    {
                        "level": 10,
                        "skill_type": 0,
                        "items": [
                            {
                                "title": "Basic Attack: Penultimate",
                                "text": "Press \u003cIconMap:Icon_Normal\u003e to activate:\\nLaunch up to four strikes forward, dealing \u003ccolor=#F0D12B\u003ePhysical DMG\u003c/color\u003e and \u003ccolor=#2EB6FF\u003eElectric DMG\u003c/color\u003e.\\nDuring the 3rd-hit, repeatedly press \u003cIconMap:Icon_Normal\u003e to continue the attack, continuously striking the enemy. Using \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eDodge\u003c/color\u003e during this period will not interrupt Qingyi's \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eBasic Attack\u003c/color\u003e combo count.\\nDuring the 3rd hit, stop pressing \u003cIconMap:Icon_Normal\u003e to interrupt the continuous attack, transitioning automatically to the 4th hit. If the continuous attack lasts for a certain time, the 4th hit will be enhanced.\\nAnti-Interrupt Level is increased and DMG received is reduced by 40% during the 3rd and 4th hit."
                            },
                            {
                                "title": "Basic Attack: Enchanted Blossoms",
                                "text": "Hold \u003cIconMap:Icon_Normal\u003e to activate:\\nLaunches a forward rush attack, dealing \u003ccolor=#2EB6FF\u003eElectric DMG\u003c/color\u003e.\\nAnti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill."
                            },
                            {
                                "title": "Flash Connect",
                                "text": "When Qingyi deals \u003ccolor=#2EB6FF\u003eElectric DMG\u003c/color\u003e with a skill, she accumulates \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eFlash Connect Voltage\u003c/color\u003e. When \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eFlash Connect Voltage\u003c/color\u003e reaches 75%, she will enter the \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eFlash Connect\u003c/color\u003e state. When using her \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eBasic Attack: Enchanted Moonlit Blossoms\u003c/color\u003e, Qingyi will consume all \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eFlash Connect Voltage\u003c/color\u003e and exit the \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eFlash Connect\u003c/color\u003e state. For every 1% of \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eFlash Connect Voltage\u003c/color\u003e consumed over 75%, her Damage and Daze inflicted by this skill will be increased by 1%/0.5%. \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eBasic Attack: Enchanted Moonlit Blossoms\u003c/color\u003e itself does not accumulate \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eFlash Connect Voltage\u003c/color\u003e."
                            },
                            {
                                "title": "Basic Attack: Enchanted Moonlit Blossoms",
                                "text": "During the \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eFlash Connect\u003c/color\u003e state, hold \u003cIconMap:Icon_Normal\u003e to activate:\\nLaunch five consecutive forward rush attacks, then execute a Finishing Move that inflicts massive \u003ccolor=#2EB6FF\u003eElectric DMG\u003c/color\u003e. Release \u003cIconMap:Icon_Normal\u003e during the move to trigger the Finishing Move early.\\nActivate the Finishing Move just before the character is attacked to trigger \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003ePerfect Dodge\u003c/color\u003e.\\nAnti-Interrupt level is increased and DMG received is reduced by 40% during the rush attack. Qingyi is invulnerable during the Finishing Move."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "level": 10,
                        "skill_type": 1,
                        "items": [
                            {
                                "title": "Special Attack: Sunlit Glory",
                                "text": "Press \u003cIconMap:Icon_Special\u003e to activate:\\nQuickly swings upward, followed by a downward smash, dealing \u003ccolor=#2EB6FF\u003eElectric DMG\u003c/color\u003e.\\nAnti-Interrupt level is increased while using this skill."
                            },
                            {
                                "title": "EX Special Attack: Moonlit Begonia",
                                "text": "With enough Energy, press \u003cIconMap:Icon_SpecialReady\u003e to activate:\\nQuickly swings upward and leaps into the air, turning around to launch a series of attacks, then follows up with a powerful downward smash, dealing massive \u003ccolor=#2EB6FF\u003eElectric DMG\u003c/color\u003e.\\nHold \u003cIconMap:Icon_SpecialReady\u003e to consume additional energy to increase the number of hits of the series of attacks.\\nCharacter is invulnerable while using this skill.\\nAfter executing the move, you can immediately follow up with the 3rd-hit of a \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eBasic Attack\u003c/color\u003e."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "level": 9,
