                                "text": "Press \u003cIconMap:Icon_Evade\u003e to activate:\\nA quick dash dodge.\\nCharacter is invulnerable while using this skill."
                            },
                            {
                                "title": "Dash Attack: Breach",
                                "text": "Press \u003cIconMap:Icon_Normal\u003e during a Dodge to activate:\\nRush forward and then launch an upward attack, dealing \u003ccolor=#F0D12B\u003ePhysical DMG\u003c/color\u003e."
                            },
                            {
                                "title": "Dodge Counter: Lingering Sentiments",
                                "text": "Press \u003cIconMap:Icon_Normal\u003e during a \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003ePerfect Dodge\u003c/color\u003e to activate:\\nLeap into the air and then perform a downward attack, dealing \u003ccolor=#2EB6FF\u003eElectric DMG\u003c/color\u003e.\\nCharacter is invulnerable while using this skill."
