                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "level": 9,
                        "skill_type": 3,
                        "items": [
                            {
                                "title": "Chain Attack: Tranquil Serenade",
                                "text": "When a \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eChain Attack\u003c/color\u003e is triggered, select the character to activate:\\nLaunch a series of powerful strikes over a large area in front, dealing massive \u003ccolor=#2EB6FF\u003eElectric DMG\u003c/color\u003e\\nWhen this attack hits an enemy, the skill's DMG increases by 3% for every stack of \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eSubjugation\u003c/color\u003e in \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eCore Passive: Eternal Seasons\u003c/color\u003e the target has.\\nCharacter is invulnerable while using this skill."
                            },
                            {
                                "title": "Ultimate: Eight Sounds of Ganzhou",
                                "text": "When Decibel Rating is at \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eMaximum\u003c/color\u003e, press \u003cIconMap:Icon_UltimateReady\u003e to activate:\\nLaunch a series of powerful strikes over a large area in front, followed by a Finishing Move, dealing massive \u003ccolor=#2EB6FF\u003eElectric DMG\u003c/color\u003e.\\nCharacter is invulnerable while using this skill."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "level": 6,
                        "skill_type": 5,
                        "items": [
                            {
                                "title": "Core Passive: Eternal Seasons",
                                "text": "When Qingyi lands a Finishing Move on an enemy with her \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eBasic Attack: Enchanted Moonlit Blossoms\u003c/color\u003e, it applies 5 stacks of \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eSubjugation\u003c/color\u003e to the enemy, stacking up to 20 times. Each stack of \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eSubjugation\u003c/color\u003e increases the target's Stun DMG Multiplier by \u003ccolor=#2BAD00\u003e3.7\u003c/color\u003e%. For each rush attack performed during \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eBasic Attack: Enchanted Moonlit Blossoms\u003c/color\u003e, the Finishing Move will apply an extra stack of \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eSubjugation\u003c/color\u003e. If \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003ePerfect Dodge\u003c/color\u003e is triggered when using the Finishing Move, it directly applies 10 stacks of \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eSubjugation\u003c/color\u003e. When applying Subjugation to normal and elite enemies, the target receives double the stacks. When the target recovers from being Stunned, the corresponding stacks of \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eSubjugation\u003c/color\u003e are reset."
                            },
                            {
                                "title": "Additional Ability: Three Verses of Farewell at Yang Pass",
                                "text": "When another character in your squad is an \u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eAttack\u003c/color\u003e character or shares the same Faction:\\n\u003ccolor=#FFFFFF\u003eBasic Attacks\u003c/color\u003e deal 20% increased Daze. If Qingyi's Impact is greater than 120, each point over increases her ATK by 6, up to a maximum of 600."
                            }
